(6, 75, 'Support by the Hour', 'support-by-the-hour', '<p><img src="images/breakfix_icon_white.png" alt="" /></p>\r\n<p>Our technicians will be there for you when you need us. </p>\r\n<p>We guarentee response times within 4 business hours of your call. Our standard business hours are between 8AM and 6PM, Monday to Friday excluding public holidays.</p>\r\n<p style="padding-bottom: 0px;">Emergency/After Hours support provided upon request.</p>\r\n', '\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td width="60"><img style="border: none;" src="images/breakfix.png" alt="" width="200" height="300" /></td>\r\n<td valign="top"> \r\n<h1>Hourly Support</h1>\r\n<p>Our technicians will be there for you when you need them, and we guarentee response times of either same day, or within 4 business hours of your call.</p>\r\n<p>We provide support on an hourly basis from 8AM to 6PM.</p>\r\n<p>This plan is ideal for those that want to engage Technical support for a single project or upgrade. There are no service agreements or on going support, we come in deploy/fix and leave. This is great way to bring in extra workers to upgrade your workstations, servers or networks without burdening your I.T. staff.</p>\r\n<p>A seperate rate is available for works outside of these hours. All jobs are billed for a minimum of 1 hour.</p>\r\n<p>Simply give us a call and we''ll be there.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<p style="text-align: center;">To Compare the different Service Packages Click <a href="index.php/support-plans">here</a></p>\r\n<p> </p>', 1, 9, '2014-09-09 03:29:08', 307, '', '2015-01-06 01:18:03', 307, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-09-09 03:29:08', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}