(25, 124, 'Upgrades and Projects', 'upgrades-and-projects', '<h1><img class="pull-left" style="border: none; padding-right: 5px;" src="images/Upgrades.jpg" alt="" width="432" height="249" />Upgrades and Projects</h1>\r\n<p>Managing your I.T. infrastructure is a demanding task all by itself.</p>\r\n<p>Finding the time and resources to improve it can be one of the biggest challengers faced by any company.</p>\r\n<p>The projects team at Sapient Technology Solutions specializes in managing the upgrade and deployment of new systems, for any size business. We can upgrade a single server through to deploying a fleet of workstations that numbering in the hundreds.</p>\r\n<p>All projects are carefully managed so that our clients has complete visibility on the progress and the time and scope or works involved to bring them to completion.</p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>Here are a few of the common projects you may find of interest:-</p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>Software package upgrades and deployment.</li>\r\n<li>Workstations Upgrades and migration.</li>\r\n<li>Server installation and setup.</li>\r\n<li>Cloud services implementation and migration.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p> </p>\r\n<p>To talk to us about your project needs please send us an email with your projects needs, or have a representative come to you to discuss your requirements.</p>', '', 1, 15, '2014-12-29 01:56:04', 307, '', '2015-01-05 21:32:13', 307, 0, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '2014-12-29 01:56:04', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '{"image_intro":"","float_intro":"","image_intro_alt":"","image_intro_caption":"","image_fulltext":"","float_fulltext":"","image_fulltext_alt":"","image_fulltext_caption":""}', '{"urla":false,"urlatext":"","targeta":"","urlb":false,"urlbtext":"","targetb":"","urlc":false,"urlctext":"","targetc":""}', '{"show_title":"","link_titles":"","show_tags":"","show_intro":"","info_block_position":"","show_category":"","link_category":"","show_parent_category":"","link_parent_category":"","show_author":"","link_author":