(421, 1, 1, '', '2015-08-27 22:53:00', 307, 6418, '059a7cbce70c45795749374452d1085d5e92753e', '{"id":1,"asset_id":"64","title":"Support Plans","alias":"need-help","introtext":"<div>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<h2 style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Support Plans<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">We\\u00a0provide I.T. support and service plans that cater for small business all the way through to international companies.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">We can tailor service plans to suit any of your needs, but to make life easier we have created 3 service plan packages.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">Each\\u00a0service plan\\u00a0has a different level of support that suits a variety of budgets.<\\/p>\\r\\n<a name=\\"comparison\\"><\\/a>\\r\\n<p style=\\"text-align: center;\\">{loadposition comparison}<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<a href=\\"#breakfix\\">\\u00a0<\\/a>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0 <a name=\\"managed\\"><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td>\\u00a0<img style=\\"border: 0;\\" src=\\"images\\/mangedservices.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"200\\" height=\\"300\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td valign=\\"top\\">\\u00a0\\r\\n<h2>From $54.00 per Device per Month<\\/h2>\\r\\nYour computers, servers, and network are the core of your business. Ensuring that they are running at their peak efficiency is the core of our managed service. It is all about preventing I.T. problems before they impact your business.\\r\\n<p>With our Managed Service Premium package we bring the latest monitoring and maintenace technology to your business for a fixed monthly price.<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>These are some of the benefits of our Service:<\\/p>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td colspan=\\"2\\">\\r\\n<h3>Proactive Monitoring<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Improve your network, computers and application reliability, up-time, availability and performance.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Minimise unexpected failures with both your hardware and applications.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Monitor hardware and software for potential failures.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Always ensure your machines have current virus and malware protection.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Ensure that your hardware has the lastest patches and security measures installed.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<h3>Fixed Monthly Costs<\\/h3>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>Reduce the actual cost of unexpected I.T. failures with all works both onsite and remote covered under the Managed Service Agreement.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Minimise opportunity costs associated with network, system or apps failures.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Reduces overall cost of I.T. functions and hardware.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>\\r\\n<p>For a comparision of our different service plans click <a href=\\"#comparison\\">here<\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<\\/tbody>\\r\\n<\\/table>\\r\\n<p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\\r\\n<hr \\/>\\r\\n<p><a name=\\"business\\"><\\/a><\\/p>\\r\\n<table>\\r\\n<tbody>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td><img style=\\"border: 0;\\" src=\\"images\\/businesssupport2.png\\" alt=\\"\\" width=\\"200\\" height=\\"300\\" \\/><\\/td>\\r\\n<td valign=\\"top\\">\\r\\n<h2>Business Support (From $13.50 per Device per Month)<\\/h2>\\r\\n<p>Your computers, servers, and network are the core of your business. Use the proven technologies offered in our Premium Support but pay at an hourly rate. <br \\/>Be assured that your computers run the latest updates &amp; Anti-Virus definitions, and that help is only ever a click away.<\\/p>\\r\\n<\\/td>\\r\\n<\\/tr>\\r\\n<tr>\\r\\n<td colspan=\\"2\\">With the Business Support Package you have:\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n<li>High Quality monitoring agent.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Pay-As-You-Go technical Support.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Guaranteed 4 hours or better onsite support.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Backup planning and reporting.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Free virus and malware protection.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>$98\\/Hour during business hours.<\\/li>\\r\\n<li>Advanced ticket and problem tracking.<\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul